{"tid":1678314,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"（盡做)一人一信CNN","createTime":"2019-10-27T15:04:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-28T08:42:03.000Z","uid":270938,"like":14,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"294e9a4fc13d5a6c076fca90393822aaf3d795c2","tid":1678314,"uid":270938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T15:04:54.000Z","msg":"踢爆'CNN 轉緊軚　形勢前所未有地差'一post係五毛組團攪事<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1678016\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1678016</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n雖然話就話CNN係fake news，但佢都係一大美國報社，即係有好多美國人會睇佢既新聞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">我地一人一信give feedback去CNN 一齊譴責佢，向佢施壓，<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">堅守美國戰線</span></span>：<br />\n<a href=\"https://edition.cnn.com/feedback\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fedition.cnn.com%2Ffeedback&d=qY%2BFdmg29Nq5PZFqoXGv4f1%2FuxKlhk2BFa%2FcJox4Q%2F4%3D&h=0c53b0bf\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fedition.cnn.com%2Ffeedback&h=29e80f8a\" target=\"_blank\">https://edition.cnn.com/feedback</a></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">Template</span></span>:<br />\n<br />\nDear Editor, <br />\n<br />\nI am a Hong Kong local resident. I would like to comment on the news published by CNN titled &quot;As violence and vandalism and escalate in Hong Kong, some protest supporters have had enough&quot; by Jessie Yeung, posted on October 27, 2019.<br />\n<br />\nIt is with much regret that it failed to reveal the truth in Hong Kong and is plainly wrong. First, public opinion is still firmly on the side of the democracy movement&rsquo;s key demands and the majority of Hongkongers with basic universal values still strive to oppose police's use of excessive force and lack of professional code. <br />\nFrom the data, over the last few months, the Centre for Communication and Public Opinion Survey of the Chinese University of Hong Kong have conducted a series of representative surveys of public attitudes toward the current protests. In the survey conducted in early August, only 39.5 per cent of 842 respondents agreed that the protesters have used excessive force; in September survey of 623 people, which was conducted right after chief executive Carrie Lam withdrew the extradition bill, that figure held steady at 39.4 per cent (Source: <a href=\"https://www.independent.co.uk/voices/hong-kong-protests-police-violence-public-opinion-polling-support-a9158061.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.independent.co.uk%2Fvoices%2Fhong-kong-protests-police-violence-public-opinion-polling-support-a9158061.html&d=qY%2BFdmg29Nq5PZFqoXGv4f1%2FuxKlhk2BFa%2FcJox4Q%2F4%3D&h=2ac6cb75\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.independent.co.uk/voices/hong-kong-protests-police-violence-public-opinion-polling-support-a9158061.html</a>)<br />\n<br />\nSecond, it is not to say the violence and vandalism should be justified, yet it is undoubtedly the last resort to urge the government from shutting their ears to the demands. Why are Hong Kong protests getting more violent? Because justice has been missing for four months. It is for the greater good of Hong Kong that we have left no choice but to destroy our homeland temporarily for the permanent better future.<br />\n<br />\nPlease clarify the points of view in the said news article and delete it before it falsely spread to other readers who genuinely want to know the true picture and continue to support Hong Kong. <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">光復香港 <br />\n時代革命</span></span>"},{"pid":"99fde487731cdec5a95a3388d097ac2d7a50a519","tid":1678314,"uid":270938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T15:05:05.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"decd22da8865464e60c6bd2d5a84b0650a59217f","tid":1678314,"uid":270938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T15:05:15.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad27e13bc24605e73b261c1c5d3c43c3181dfd95","tid":1678314,"uid":270938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T15:05:33.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7afb1b464f754b6d00ff47c7a1eb184453fa804","tid":1678314,"uid":270938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T15:05:49.000Z","msg":"點解P牌咁難推？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a341dadf6ddbf866707aa2b3ae591b0f6e5d83c","tid":1678314,"uid":270938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T15:06:19.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2342483a0b831254f88225cc348670ab0d27805","tid":1678314,"uid":31151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T15:06:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff2e6414c90d1ebe17022ba5b0da4ec3d81fc347","tid":1678314,"uid":270938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"sc